des: Are you Ocra enough? Welcome to the OcraVerse, in this skill listen to random ocra calls from the Amazon Sustainability Data Initiative, The OcraSound repository, classified into clicks for echolocation, whistles and calls, mimic them and then try to understand live ocra sounds from the ocra net. http://www.orca-live.net/
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
